    {
      "name": "Hourly Metrics (Hiệu suất theo giờ)",
      "description": "## 🆕 Hiệu suất theo giờ\n\nEndpoint mới — lấy dữ liệu sản lượng, nhân viên, và máy in theo giờ từ FPlatform.\n\n**Auth:** 🔒 Private — cần Bearer Token\n**Permission:** `shifts.index` hoặc role `admin`\n\n### Team × Metric Compatibility\n\n| Team | productivity | staff_count | staff_productivity | machine_productivity |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| in | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |\n| cat | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| pick | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| mockup | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| pack_ship | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| dtg_print | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |\n| dtg_pick | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n\n### Timezone\n\nTham số `start_shift` và `end_shift` dùng timezone **US/Central** (múi giờ xưởng).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Hourly Productivity — Team In",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{API_URL}}/v1/admin/fplatform/hourly-metrics?team=print&metric=productivity&start_shift=2026-04-14 06:00:00&end_shift=2026-04-14 14:00:00",
              "host": ["{{API_URL}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "admin", "fplatform", "hourly-metrics"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "team", "value": "in", "description": "Required. in, cat, pick, mockup, pack_ship, dtg_print, dtg_pick" },
                { "key": "metric", "value": "productivity", "description": "Required. productivity, staff_count, staff_productivity, machine_productivity" },
                { "key": "start_shift", "value": "2026-04-14 06:00:00", "description": "Required. Shift start (US/Central)" },
                { "key": "end_shift", "value": "2026-04-14 14:00:00", "description": "Required. Shift end (US/Central)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "🔒 **Private** — Sản lượng team IN theo giờ.\n\nĐếm `SUM(total_file)` từ `user_group_scan` với `work_type=0, work_status=1`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — Productivity",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"team\": \"in\",\n    \"metric\": \"productivity\",\n    \"hours\": [\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 06\", \"value\": 125 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 07\", \"value\": 340 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 08\", \"value\": 285 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 09\", \"value\": 310 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 10\", \"value\": 298 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 11\", \"value\": 275 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 12\", \"value\": 320 },\n      { \"date_hour\": \"2026-04-14 13\", \"value\": 305 }\n    ]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
